<p>Apple</p>

<p>Apple offers various software development tools and technologies that can be used to create high-end software solutions for businesses. Apple's software development platforms are known for their user-friendly interface and efficient performance, making them a popular choice among developers and businesses.</p>
<h3>Features:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Xcode Integrated Development Environment (IDE) for building macOS, iOS, watchOS, and tvOS applications.</li>
    <li>Swift programming language for creating scalable and high-performance applications.</li>
    <li>Objective-C programming language for creating native applications for macOS and iOS.</li>
    <li>Apple Developer Program providing tools, resources, and support for app development.</li>
    <li>Core ML framework for developing machine learning models and integrating them into Apple apps.</li>
    <li>ARKit framework for creating augmented reality experiences on iOS devices.</li>
    <li>Apple Pay and In-App Purchase APIs for integrating payment processing into apps.</li>
</ul>